t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A m\u00e1quina de enchimento de desodorizante Npack \u00e9 um tipo de equipamento de enchimento, que se adapta \u00e0 tecnologia avan\u00e7ada de enchimento a quente, o processo de trabalho \u00e9 tipicamente de enchimento a quente, a f\u00f3rmula s\u00f3lida \u00e9 derretida, depois dispensada no barril vazio, ap\u00f3s o enchimento, uma esta\u00e7\u00e3o de resfriamento (t\u00fanel de resfriamento) solidifica-o antes de tampar. O controlo preciso do volume \u00e9 normalmente conseguido com uma enchedora de pist\u00e3o, que tamb\u00e9m \u00e9 acionada por um servo motor.<\/p><p>A m\u00e1quina foi concebida para trocas r\u00e1pidas entre diferentes tamanhos de contentores e linhas de produtos; f\u00e1cil opera\u00e7\u00e3o e limpeza; \u00e9 adequada para encher l\u00edquidos quentes ou viscosos.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e6fd310 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2e6fd310\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-211b2ccb elementor-widget elementor-widget-video\" data-id=\"211b2ccb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;youtube_url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/youtu.be\\\/jo0OqbwteRc&quot;,&quot;show_image_overlay&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;image_overlay&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/www.npackpm.com\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2025\\\/10\\\/2025101510050893.webp&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:2803,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;tube filling and sealing machine&quot;,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;library&quot;},&quot;video_type&quot;:&quot;youtube&quot;,&quot;controls&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"video.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-wrapper elementor-open-inline\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-video\"><\/div>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-custom-embed-image-overlay\" style=\"background-image: url(https: