ype=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFuncionamento f\u00e1cil\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tAp\u00f3s anos de desenvolvimento, o programa HMI e PLC \u00e9 muito f\u00e1cil para qualquer novo utilizador\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7caff8f9 brown-hover e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7caff8f9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-39d77b46 elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"39d77b46\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tEspa\u00e7o de pegada\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\ta m\u00e1quina de enchimento de desodorizantes apenas necessita de um pequeno espa\u00e7o com menos de 1,5 metros quadrados\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-78c6a647 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"78c6a647\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4d7ae533 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4d7ae533\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6271ab51 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6271ab51\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Como funciona uma m\u00e1quina de enchimento de desodorizantes?<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eda88cc elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"eda88cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-400afe33 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"400afe33\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>O procedimento de trabalho de uma m\u00e1quina de enchimento de desodorizantes \u00e9 um processo sistem\u00e1tico, passo a passo, concebido para garantir a precis\u00e3o, efici\u00eancia e seguran\u00e7a do produto. \u00c9 adaptado para lidar com diferentes tipos de desodorizantes - pastas adesivas, l\u00edquidos roll-on e solu\u00e7\u00f5es em spray - enquanto adere aos princ\u00edpios de enchimento \u00e0 temperatura ambiente e dosagem de pist\u00e3o. Abaixo est\u00e1 o fluxo de trabalho detalhado e padronizado da opera\u00e7\u00e3o:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11dc0e00 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"11dc0e00\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c7a55f5 e-grid e-con-full e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c7a55f5\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4de90213 brown-hover e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4de90213\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20c07b9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"20c07b9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t1. prepara\u00e7\u00e3o do material\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tUtilizar a bomba automaticamente Transfira o material desodorizante pr\u00e9-misturado para a tremonha da m\u00e1quina de enchimento. Para pastas de desodorizante em stick espessas, inicie o sistema de aquecimento e agita\u00e7\u00e3o suave da tremonha para manter a homogeneidade e evitar a segrega\u00e7\u00e3o dos ingredientes; para l\u00edquidos roll-on ou spray de baixa viscosidade, salte a agita\u00e7\u00e3o, mas certifique-se de que o material est\u00e1 livre de impurezas.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6bce6256 brown-hover e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6bce6256\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6629c722 elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"6629c722\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t2. defini\u00e7\u00e3o dos par\u00e2metros\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t Introduzir os par\u00e2metros de produ\u00e7\u00e3o no sistema de controlo de acordo com as especifica\u00e7\u00f5es do produto desodorizante, se definido anteriormente, pode simplesmente adaptar a f\u00f3rmula.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7a0b239e brown-hover e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7a0b239e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c5330fd elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"5c5330fd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t3.Carregamento e transporte de contentores vazios\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tColocar os recipientes vazios de desodorizante (tubos de stick, frascos roll-on, latas de spray) no tabuleiro de alimenta\u00e7\u00e3o da m\u00e1quina ou no transportador diretamente, depende das carater\u00edsticas dos recipientes. Assegurar que os recipientes de embalagem est\u00e3o limpos, secos e sem deforma\u00e7\u00f5es.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-60f76807 brown-hover e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"60f76807\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-441e9ec1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"441e9ec1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t4. enchimento\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-icon-box-description\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tO sensor de garrafa detecta os recipientes de alimenta\u00e7\u00e3o e, em seguida, enche e dosa automaticamente o l\u00edquido no recipiente, o sistema de dosagem \u00e9 adaptado com tecnologia volum\u00e9trica de pist\u00e3o e o curso funciona atrav\u00e9s de um servo motor.\t\t\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7384fad7 brown-hover e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7384fad7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2ca331e4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\" data-id=\"2ca331e4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-icon-box-content\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-icon-box-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span  >